---
title: Honey & Thyme Glazed Pork with Cheesy-Mashed Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: The only thing better than mashed potato is mashed potato plus cheese! This hearty side becomes creamy, rich and extra warming with the addition of flavoursome Parmesan. Add sweet and herby pork loin steaks and crisp, nutty veggies and this delicious dinner plate will get five stars!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c7f5262e3f33912af4c4122-ec8eb5d5.jpg
